        %h1 What is HIPAA Compliant Email?
        %p
          The
          %a{:href => "https://www.paubox.com/blog/hipaa-privacy-rule-business-associates", :onclick => "__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'https://www.paubox.com/blog/hipaa-privacy-rule-business-associates', 'HIPAA Privacy Rule');", :rel => "nofollow"} HIPAA Privacy Rule
